userUtterance.text: can i see my payment history

requestBody.query: can i see my payment history

200.answer: Yes, from the Menu, select Your Account and then select "Transactions". You will see a list of all Payment history as well as any other types of transactions.

snippets.text: Q: Can I See My Transactions or Payment History? A: Yes, from the Menu, select Your Account and then select "Transactions". You will see a list of all Payment history as well as any other types of transactions.
snippets.title: FAQDONE2

agentUtterance.text: Yes, from the Menu, select Your Account and then select "Transactions". You will see a list of all Payment history as well as any other types of transactions.
The payment amount is the total cost of the payment.
The status is the current state of the payment. It can be listed as processing, complete, or declined.
